  "description": "Horizontal tab bar container that wraps a set of Tabulation_Cells instances separated by vertical line dividers. Scroll type=None (fixed layout). The bar handles the outer frame, inner padding, and divider chrome; individual cell selection state (active/rest) is delegated to the Tabulation_Cells sub-component.",
